Scripts to stream Video from Pi Camera to Remote Client using UDP and TCP. The streamed Video will be shown in a Video Player. This Scripts are for Demonstration Purposes. 

Usage Server:
./<Scriptname>_udp/tcp <IP>
Usage Client:
./<Scriptname>_udp/tcp <IP>

To show the Stream MPlayer is used by the Scripts. MPlayer can be installed on debian Machines using 'sudo apt-get install mplayer mplayer-gui'.
